org.gephi.data.attributes.type

Class DynamicInteger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gephi.data.attributes.type.DynamicType<Integer>
      • org.gephi.data.attributes.type.DynamicInteger

  • public final class DynamicInteger
extends DynamicType<Integer>
    Represents Integer type which can have got different values in different time intervals.
    Author:
    Cezary Bartosiak
